Makes a release to GitHub
Usage: polyglot-release [OPTIONS] MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH
OPTIONS:
  --help                              shows this help
  --no-git-push                       do not push to git
  --no-git-commit                     do not commit git
  --only-release                      do not update versions after release
  --quiet                             don't log progress messages
  --release-branch-template=TEMPLATE  use TEMPLATE for release branch to push to. Include <new-version> to
                                      substitute the new release's version number.
                                      default: release/v<new-version>
